data.name: CLOSED SUCTION CATHETER
data.description:
## COMPOSITION
- 100% PVC and 100% DEHP-FREE PVC

## STERILIZATION
- Ethylene Oxide (EO) Sterile

## PRESENTATIONS
- Soft PVC and DEHP-FREE PVC
- Latex-free
- Color-Coded Size Identification

## PERFORMANCE
- Reliable protection against accidental vacuum activation with a special locking button
- Freely rotating connectors with a double ball-and-socket design

## ANESTHASIA
